card_description:
COMMENTS TREND
Shows the total number of people who have made comments on the group home page. Identify the reasons for spikes in comments so you don't miss out on important details pertaining to group events.

collection: Meetup Pulse: Your different group activities at a glance.
card_description:
RECENT RSVPs
Shows your groups that have recently received RSVP confirmations. Keep track of group events and plan accordingly.

MEMBERS
Shows the total number of members for your group broken down by state. Consider finding ways to grow your group network to multiple states.

collection: Specific Group Activity: Quick insight into upcoming events and activity
card_description:
NEW MEMBERS TREND
Shows the number of people who have joined your group over time. Consider finding ways to promote your group to increase membership.

collection: Specific Group Demographics: Where do group members live and what are their interests?
card_description:
MEMBERS' HOMETOWN
Shows the hometown of all your group members. Find ways to diversify your group members.

card_description:
MEMBER BIOS / INTERESTS
Shows the biographies for all your group members. Increase engagement and learn about your group demographics by becoming familiar with member interests and bios.

collection: Meetup Pulse: Your different group activities at a glance.
card_description:
ACTIVITY FOR ALL YOUR GROUPS
Shows who has joined, RSVP'd, uploaded a photo or commented on photos for all your groups. Consider welcoming new members who have joined your various groups.

collection: Specific Group Activity: Quick insight into upcoming events and activity
card_description:
GROUP PHOTOS
Shows all the photos that have been posted for your group. Share or take down photos as needed.

collection: Specific Group Demographics: Where do group members live and what are their interests?

Provides a list of all your members. Consider reaching out and welcoming new members to your group.

collection: Meetup Pulse: Your different group activities at a glance.
card_description:

Shows the number of new members joining all your groups. Identify the reason(s) for spikes in new members for certain groups.

collection: Specific Group Activity: Quick insight into upcoming events and activity
card_description:
SCHEDULED EVENTS
Shows the number of events for the group you specified when installing the QuickStart. Use this information to help plan your schedule.

collection: Meetup Pulse: Your different group activities at a glance.
card_description:
CONFIRMED RSVPs
Shows the number of people who have RSVP'd to group events in which you are also a member. Increase your Meet Up network by attending events that are likely to draw big crowds.

card_description:
